products.title: Valencia Simplicity Beige Vertical Blind
products.metadescription:
This valenica simplicity vertical blind is light beige, just like an extremely milky coffee. Some might say buff or ecru but whatever you call it, it's a nice neutral colour that adds just enough tone to your window. 
  
Its got a contemporary flavour and won't look out of place

products.title: Valencia Parchment Vertical Blind
products.metadescription: This valencia parchment vertical blind is a light neutral with and organic flavour. It will work well in a whole host of settings and does a great job of making your space feel open. The light filtering fabric stops the glare while still allowing light to brighten up your space,
